<p><a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5905855/pdf/lgbt.2017.0011.pdf" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:10pt"><span style="font-family:Arial"><u>Targeted Victimization and Suicidality Among Trans People: A Web-Based Survey</u></span></span></span></a></p>

